ss=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60d0d6e85526c8406f5862387ce512144348886","tid":446181,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做下運動會頭腦清醒D<br />\n我呢幾日都差唔多情況</blockquote><br />\n每日嘅lunch time係最多嘢諗<br />\n我都打算緊明天食完飯去跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef2b6e6fba7f2f453693fac9fe1261115992497","tid":446181,"uid":130287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唉 見到一個好朋友拍拖 個心唔上唔下 <br />\n好驚見到佢拖住個男仔 我唔識點面對佢 要係佢面前扮到無野真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好朋友？你確定嗎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我連自己想點都唔知 可唔可以教我點做"},{"pid":"8a9d978eed41c5c4ec3b4db36367152a243c97c5","tid":446181,"uid":124140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做下運動會頭腦清醒D<br />\n我呢幾日都差唔多情況</blockquote><br />\n每日嘅lunch time係最多嘢諗<br />\n我都打算緊明天食完飯去跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係一到半夜屋企人訓曬就開始諗未來點行、要點搵工、由6月開始過左幾耐近乎廢青生活、聽日要點過，唔會訓唔著但個腦好亂<br />\n到左臨界點就做運動發洩下，清醒完再繼續搵辦法解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 飯後散步就算，跑步小心胃痛"},{"pid":"7d0a2f080f933b9f443cfd8498f9a3e855bbd26c","tid":446181,"uid":99259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:41:31.000Z","msg":"做運動都係個幾好嘅選擇減下壓,你識放鬆自己而唔係鑽牛角尖已經好好啦. 證明你都識為自己諗下,嘗試俾自己專注係其他事上面呀. 有時做野做到麻木曬,會忘記咗當初嘅目標,但唔代表以後都揾唔翻向前嘅動力架. 其實你啱呀,可能大家每日都過緊類似嘅生活,會覺得厭倦, 但點樣係日常生活中揾到快樂先係重點呀, 未必係好複雜嘅事, 例如我會聽下自己鐘意嘅歌, 遊下車河周圍去之類. 每日俾自己放鬆十幾分鐘,已經可以令自已正面好多. 你有冇咩係以前好想但試一直冇做到？試下揾翻以前嘅自己,突破下自己揾D新嘗試,或者可以揾到新出口呢"},{"pid":"01c472dfc1833c1d567033f44790a48c152ecaf3","tid":446181,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以為我自己打"},{"pid":"386424b394f51226395bb36b6baed40de9c4f198","tid":446181,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T18:49:59.000Z","msg":"不過見到咁多人係咁  知道唔係自己問題 好過啲<br />\n可能 人就根本係咁 擁有左既唔會望 望啲失去/未擁有既<br />\n所以 好正常架喂 大家一齊唔好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n展望下啲值得期待既事"},{"pid":"e941a5c6f9f14da5bd7f8bc1be086db60f637161","tid":446181,"uid":8598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一入嚟以為篇嘢係我打嘅<br />\n樓主寫嘅正正係近排嘅感受<br />\n會突然間好想好想free fall</blockquote><br />\n這裡有我G持呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5a3b64f87ef8865714728da42591199dcb80b9","tid":446181,"uid":78863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T05:52:29.000Z","msg":"我都以為係自己打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a59ae4caa998a16e31fea94eba4d9137aafcd34","tid":446181,"uid":137847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"以為自己打啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a697eef921cd1fa34d09eabddd7c0a3431762f","tid":446181,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T06:35:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為自己打啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔幾日就黎一次<br />\n好難頂<br />\n完全唔知點解<br />\n無啦啦發現自己喊緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}